{% extends "layouts/doc-layout" %}

{% block title %}Uniq Filter - Wisp Template Documentation{% end %}

{% block body %}
<h1>Uniq Filter</h1>

<p>Removes duplicate values from an array, keeping the first occurrence of each value.</p>

<h2>Syntax</h2>
<pre><code>{% raw %}
{{ array | uniq }}
{% endraw %}</code></pre>

<h2>Examples</h2>
<pre><code>{% raw %}
{% assign tags = "go,web,go,api,web" | split: "," %}
{{ tags | uniq | join: ", " }}
{% endraw %}</code></pre>
<p><strong>Output:</strong> go, web, api</p>

<pre><code>{% raw %}
{% assign nums = "1,2,2,3,1,4" | split: "," %}
{{ nums | uniq | join: " " }}
{% endraw %}</code></pre>
<p><strong>Output:</strong> 1 2 3 4</p>

<h2>Notes</h2>
<p>Uniqueness is determined by string representation of each value. The first occurrence of each value is kept; subsequent duplicates are removed. The original order is preserved.</p>

<h2>See Also</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href="/docs/filters/sort">sort</a></li>
  <li><a href="/docs/filters/size">size</a></li>
</ul>
{% end %}
